title: Digital Grampa 2000 - Dreams In Dial-Up: 56.66k
description:
Well, though the albums been out for a while, Ive been slacking getting it up here. This EP is much shorter than my last release, but I like to think that this is much tighter and more fun to listen to than Penny Pony Rides.

Denvertronic.com said: "Another fab release from Digital Grampa 2000. A little noise, a little gabber, a little industrial, with a pinch of self destruction and youve got the ingredients for a good time. I agree: screw generic dance music. Rock on with your bad self."

Album is sampled in high-bitrate mp3 and comes bundled with original artwork by System Override, and other goodies.

Track listing:
01. Connection Established Message 001
02. Loading Please Wait
03. Program Execute (50%)
04. Program Execute (100%)
05. Some Sick
06. Twisted Fuck
07. Came On The Keyboard
08. And Didnt Clean Up Afterwards
09. So Now
10. My Fingers
11. Taste Delicious
12. And Im Happy
13. Connection Terminated Message 244

Enjoy!
